               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Taʾāmra Māryām "Miracles of Mary" (fols. 1ra-123vb)&#xD; I-1) Maṣḥafa
                     śǝrʿāt, Introductory rite of al-Muʿallaqah (fols. 1ra-3vb)&#xD; I-2)
                     Introductory exhortation and hymns (fols. 3vb-6vb)&#xD; I-3) ʾƎsaggǝd laki
                     wa-ʾǝweddǝsaki... “I worship Thee…” (fols. 6vb-7va)&#xD; I-4a) Taʾāmra Māryām
                     "Miracles of Mary": 52 miracles (fols. 7va-91vb, 93ra-vb), incomplete?&#xD;
                     I-5) ʾAkkonu bǝʾsi... "Does not the man..." (distributed among the miracles of
                     Mary, fols. 11ra-24vb, 37ra-39rb, 49ra-56vb, 72vb-83va)&#xD; I-4b) Taʾāmra
                     Māryām "Miracles of Mary": 40 miracles (fols. 92ra-vb, 94ra-123vb),
                     incomplete</summary>
               </msContents>
